{"tid":1585541,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"按目前發展路線，下一組拘捕對象係記者","createTime":"2019-09-21T15:49:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T03:03:20.000Z","uid":206523,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7af35730be1e10e7cd14338738e07a25f875c1a0","tid":1585541,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:49:55.000Z","msg":"黑警拘捕進化路線：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">零散拘捕<br />\n⬇️<br />\n前線勇武<br />\n⬇️<br />\n和理非<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: small;\">八區開花 黃大仙合法集會地點零衝突下拘捕</span></em></span><br />\n⬇️<br />\n議員<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: small;\">不論區議員、立法會議員</span></em></span><br />\n⬇️<br />\n路人 / 市民<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: small;\">多單新聞，唔多解釋</span></em></span><br />\n⬇️<br />\n急救員<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><em><span style=\"font-size: small;\">今日</span></em></span><br />\n⬇️<br />\n<strong>記者</strong><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解估下一個對象係記者？理由好簡單：<br />\n<br />\n黑警憎記者已經係眾所周知<br />\n因為直播影到好多真相，佢哋係鏡頭下被牽制<br />\n佢哋一直想拉記者群好耐，只係仲未啱timing<br />\n<br />\n前排已大肆吹噓有假記者<br />\n又搵大陸人扮記者  故意被記者影到  捏造事實<br />\n呢兩種行為都係為「合法」拉記者而鋪好曬路<br />\n<br />\n我唔知幾時會拉，但其實呢個濫權環境底下<br />\n今次光明正大拉咗一堆急救員<br />\n下次要拉記者，只要「莫須有」罪名<br />\n<em><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">即係 非法集結、阻差辦公、協助罪犯等等，九唔搭八嘅罪名</span></span></em><br />\n<br />\n老實講，諗下班黑警如果真係拉咗班記者<br />\n佢哋會有咩後果？會動亂？會被勇武升級？<br />\n會有外國譴責？犯人權法？<br />\n答案係乜都唔會，係 <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無後果</span></strong><br />\n你覺得班黑警真係會驚外國制裁？<br />\n對佢哋嚟講，毫無威脅。<br />\n<br />\n我真係唔知幾時會拉，但我知道<br />\n當記者被拘捕的日子來臨<br />\n我哋被清算的日子都一同降臨<br />\n因為到時除咗面對衝突果班人<br />\n世界上再無人知道真相<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">以後單單都係8&middot;31</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b2f26bb3c60b359d64e6982a2bed7107ceb61397","tid":1585541,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:50:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dc66e658296f2fdc0c3e256556deed989a28c370","tid":1585541,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:50:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8b6366ebcf8feb96f4e48861f936c64f5dbee3e9","tid":1585541,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:51:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1bac7ac6b25b4056972d0719bd02fb6872a3620d","tid":1585541,"uid":259675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:51:54.000Z","msg":"記者試過 不過係大公報<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76eedf34d8ab7c615bbe965e36377fc736b322bc","tid":1585541,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:52:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cdbc080a1e81754538be88a4b5b658c66c7b0532","tid":1585541,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:52:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n 【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"fde12d6d9a97be1dd7a099f01a1489301c349241","tid":1585541,"uid":206523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:52:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8ff930f249b997a740254048bf97945b191f218c","tid":1585541,"uid":281756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:53:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"db11225536b6bf9c4ab1ee4d73974b0db7737007","tid":1585541,"uid":281756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:53:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0c51203c4e0137da00eff7b2d4f52632919e07a","tid":1585541,"uid":281756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:53:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d5ab492603e3a0afcaf4fbe01f074c6298eba54a","tid":1585541,"uid":281756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T15:53:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"